high_descs: Turn left then walk towards the sink
Pick up the spoon in the sink
Turn right then head to the coffee maker on your right
Put the spoon in the mug
Pick up the mug with spoon
Turn right then head to the sink
Put the mug with spoon in the sink
anns.task_desc: Put the mug with spoon in the sink

high_descs: Turn and go to the sink.
Pick up a spoon in the sink.
Turn and go to the coffee machine.
Put the spoon in the coffee cup on the coffee machine.
Pick up the coffee cup on the coffee machine.
Turn and go to the sink.
Put the coffee cup in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a coffee cup with a spoon to the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink.
Take the spoon out of the sink.
Turn to the left  and then left again. Walk across the kitchen to the coffee maker,
Place the spoon inside the mug in the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug and spoon from the coffee maker.
Turn right and then another right. Walk to the sink.
Place the mug and spoon in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug and spoon to the sink.
